{
  "stem": "5388.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember once, and the-- when the farmers used to catch that somebody's behind, they used to take with their whip that they used for the horse, and hit you so you would get off the-- the-- the sleigh.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember we run off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he asked, [YIDDISH], whose are you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, Gitki.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Gitki, meaning my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, no, Gitki, [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If it's Gitki, sit down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then come in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I never forgot that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, that is a good one, so a good question.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you see, that shows you the love and affection that Mother had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember, too, Mother was very ill at one time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a mass was said in the Catholic church on her behalf, for her to-- It was almost unheard of.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I never heard of that anyplace on the subject.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But she had a mass said for her, for her health.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So she was quite generous and known in the whole place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- but this one with that farmer, [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Whose are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Gitki?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Sit down!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was arrive home with a big show.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those others were off, running off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here, I got a ride in that sleigh like a prince.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six kilometers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to the border once.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just up to the border, the Poland border was in a village called Lipowska-- L-I-P-O-W-S-K-A, Lipowska.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was six kilometers from our little town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember in '38, they were talking already, something about [INAUDIBLE] or something was-- it's-- it's-- it's the trains they used to collect money for defense.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't know what the-- I know that was in the-- the Jewish community was contributing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And people used to come with the Rabbi.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
